<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352236' id='t-352236'>So I decided to focus</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='353941' id='t-353941'>on using data and analytics</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='356158' id='t-356158'>to help make the most critical decision</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='358519' id='t-358519'>in public safety,</span>
